data.description: Absolutely Beautiful Home in Highly Desired Traditions of Braselton Golf Community, located on the 5th Golf Hole with Wonderful views of a Pond with a Fountain. The main level features an Awesome Master Suite, Family Living Area, Keeping Room, and Gourmet Kitchen. Upstairs Features 4 Spacious Bedrooms, 2 Full Jack and Jill Baths. The Basement is partially finished which is great for Entertaining Guest. The Lawn is Professionally maintained, and the Community has a Great Amenities with a Jr. Olympic Pool. Tennis and Pickle Ball courts.
